    this.collide = function (node) {
      var r = node.size + 22,
        nx1 = node.x - r,
        nx2 = node.x + r,
        ny1 = node.y - r,
        ny2 = node.y + r;
      return function (quad, x1, y1, x2, y2) {

        if (quad.point && (quad.point !== node)) {
          x = node.x - quad.point.x;
          y = node.y - quad.point.y;
          l = Math.sqrt(x * x + y * y);

          Iif (l < r) {

            node.x -= x *= l;

            quad.point.x += x;
            quad.point.y += y;
          }
        }
        return x1 > nx2 || x2 < nx1 || y1 > ny2 || y2 < ny1;
      };
    };
